title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Boeing 787 - VNAV settings (AAU 2)
description:
In this video we will look how to program the VNAV settings in the Boeing 787 after AAU2 (at the time of recording in beta). VNAV is one of the items which has been completely revised which makes it from my perspective a useful system especially when comparing it to the initial implementation.
